oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Kinsall posing next to the 5th Marine Division Memorial on Mount Suribachi, Iwo Jima
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Slide film (or reversal film) of Kinsall posing next to the 5th Marine Division Memorial on Mount Suribachi, Iwo Jima. The memorial was erected on the spot where Joe Rosenthal's famous photograph "Raising the Flag on Iwo Jima" was taken.
